<p>She graduated from Boğaziçi University Department of Sociology in 1997. She took part in many projects on reputation management during her work in marketing communications and brand management departments of respected organizations of Turkey. She has 18 years of experience in marketing communications and brand management. In 2008, she cocreated a social responsibility project with Mother Child Education Foundation for the international finance organization that she was working at. Within this project to support preschool education in disadvantaged regions of İstanbul, she also organized volunteers. That is how she started volunteering in many projects on a personal level. When she was trying to discover what she can do towards social and economic development, she met İbrahim Betil in 2011 and became a founding board member of SEN DE GEL. She is still working as a communications and brand consultant.</p>